      <talk_question mid="48"><![CDATA[<html>$Warp Helper Tracy$<BR>
To enhance an item's power, other than using potential, you can also use a method called<FONT color=#a82424>enhancement</FONT>.<BR>
You can enhance 7 types of weapons and armours for different parts of the body but not accessories.</html>]]></talk_question>
