   <talk_paragraph index="n101_event_tracey-1-b" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n101_event_tracey-1-c" mid="115" select_type="0"><![CDATA[<html>(Continue)</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="114"><![CDATA[<html>$Warp Helper Tracy$<BR>
Following the part of the body the item is equipped on, the enhancement will increase the <FONT color=#a82424>physical/magical attack power</FONT> <FONT color=#a82424>for weapons</FONT>, and increase <FONT color=#a82424>HP</FONT> and <FONT color=#a82424>MP</FONT> for <FONT color=#a82424>armours</FONT>.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n101_event_tracey-1-c" image="" itemindex="" portrait_left="" portrait_right="" center_image="">
